Operation Dudula leader, Nhlanhla 'Lux' Dlamini, has been arrested. His arrest stems from a Soweto operation over the weekend. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Operation Dudula leader Nhlanhla 'Lux' Dlamini has been arrested. Dlamini is being held at the Johannesburg Central Police Station. READ: Operation Dudula leader Nhlanhla 'Lux' Dlamini has been arrested Soweto resident Victor Ramerafe opened a case against Lux after his home was allegedly ransacked by Operation Dudula members over the weekend. Watch the video above as Dlamini speaks on his arrest.